ROUTER_REPORT_ENDAdded `crates/ajax-web/web/e2e/shell-characterization.test.ts` with two characterization tests against the current Svelte `App`:

1. **Update banner** — stateful `/api/version` mock (A on first read, B on later polls); banner becomes visible and reloads on tap.
2. **Pull-to-refresh** — touch-drag past threshold on the dashboard outlet triggers another `/api/cockpit` fetch (mobile-webkit only).

Verification passed:
- **mobile-webkit**: 2 passed
- **desktop-chromium**: 1 passed, 1 skipped (pull-to-refresh)

No production or fixture changes. One implementation note: version strings are inlined in the init script because passing `VERSION_A`/`VERSION_B` through `addInitScript` did not produce distinct responses in WebKit.
